\end_inset

 与 
\begin_inset Formula $q$
\end_inset

 是取自 
\begin_inset Formula $(1,+\infty)$
\end_inset

 的共轭指数，且 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

 与 
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

 均为非负实数，则
