\begin_layout Proof
固定 
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

，分析关于 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

 的函数 
\begin_inset Formula $f(x)=x^{p}/p+y^{q}/q-xy$
\end_inset

 的单调性、极值点：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f'(x_{*})=x_{*}^{p-1}-y=0\implies x_{*}=y^{1/(p-1)}=y^{q/p}\implies f''(x_{*})=(p-1)x_{*}^{p-2}>0
\]

\end_inset

故 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{*}=y^{q/p}$
\end_inset

 是极小值点，代入 
\begin_inset Formula $f(x)$
\end_inset

 即得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
0=f(y^{q/p})\le f(x)=x^{p}/p+y^{q}/q-xy\qquad\forall x\in[0,+\infty)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
